# Product Requirements Document: Dehumidifier Controller

> **⚠️ DOCUMENTATION MAINTENANCE REQUIRED**: This PRD must be kept synchronized with `README.md` and the codebase. See Section 8.1 for maintenance requirements and checklist. Any code changes must include corresponding documentation updates.

